@startuml StateDiagram-Material

title State Diagram: Lifecycle Materi/Lesson

[*] --> Created : Admin membuat materi

state Created {
  [*] --> Draft
  Draft : is_admin = 1
  Draft : serial_id = NULL
  Draft : Belum dibagikan ke kelas
}

Created --> Shared : Guru membagikan\nke kelas tertentu

state Shared {
  state "Dibagikan ke Kelas" as SharedToClasses
  
  SharedToClasses : Relasi via pivot table
  SharedToClasses : lesson_classroom
  
  state "Update Sharing" as UpdateShare {
    [*] --> CheckClassrooms
    CheckClassrooms --> AddClasses : Tambah kelas baru
    CheckClassrooms --> RemoveClasses : Hapus kelas
    AddClasses --> Synced
    RemoveClasses --> Synced
    Synced --> [*]
  }
  
  SharedToClasses --> UpdateShare : Guru update\npilihan kelas
}

Shared --> NotShared : Hapus semua\nsharing (sync([]))

state NotShared {
  [*] --> Available
  Available : Materi masih ada
  Available : Tapi tidak dibagikan\nke kelas manapun
}

NotShared --> Shared : Bagikan lagi

Shared --> Deleted : Admin hapus materi
NotShared --> Deleted : Admin hapus materi
Created --> Deleted : Admin hapus materi

Deleted --> [*]

note right of Shared
  Ketika materi dibagikan:
  - Pivot table lesson_classroom
    berisi record relasi
  - Guru bisa lihat badge
    "Dibagikan ke X Kelas"
  - Siswa di kelas tersebut
    bisa akses materi
end note

note right of UpdateShare
  Laravel sync() method:
  1. Hapus relasi lama
  2. Insert relasi baru
  3. Atomic operation
end note

@enduml
